items.sentence: I suspect Tom and Mary are hiding something from me.
I can't believe that you're talking to me like this.
Tom told Mary that he thought that she was an idiot.
I thought that I told you to handle this yourselves.
I just thought that you might want something to eat.
Maybe Tom thought that you wouldn't want to see him.
Proper qualifications are required for the position.
This restaurant is famous for its excellent cuisine.
Tom said that he saw something strange in the woods.
From that day on, he'll never say hello to me again.
